name: Dreams of AUX (i fell inside the monitor screen)
description:
A dream inside a monitor screen. Celebration of AUX. A world in a glass cube inside a dream. A dream inside a cube. Upon waking, we are no different. The dream life is with us. The waking world is the dream. Our oceans are made of static. 

Animated, edited, and created by Sky Goodman
Music by Quold Presents

31 second audio visual experience 

1280 x 1280 pixels
